---
// Standalone Landing Page Configuration
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/panoromics-logo.png" />
		<title>PanorOmics | Precision Medicine & Multi-Omics Integration</title>
		<style>
			/* Setup a clean, dark canvas matching your brand logo background color */
			html, body {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				box-sizing: border-box;
				background-color: #000c1a;
				color: #ffffff;
				font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
				scroll-behavior: smooth;
			}

			.page-container {
				width: 100%;
				min-height: 100vh;
			}

			/* Hero Frame Context */
			.hero-block {
				min-height: 100vh;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
				align-items: center;
				padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			.center-content {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 3.5rem;
				width: 100%;
			}

			.logo-box {
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 480px;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
				animation: revealAnim 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) both;
			}

			.main-brand-asset {
				width: 100%;
				height: auto;
				display: block;
				object-fit: contain;
			}

			/* Call to Action Capsule Buttons */
			.cta-row {
				display: flex;
				gap: 1.25rem;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				justify-content: center;
				animation: revealAnim 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s both;
			}

			.nav-button {
				font-size: 0.95rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				text-decoration: none;
				padding: 0.9rem 2.5rem;
				border-radius: 50px;
				transition: all 0.2s ease;
				letter-spacing: 0.2px;
			}

			.accent-fill {
				background-color: #1a8cff;
				color: #ffffff;
				box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(26, 140, 255, 0.2);
			}

			.accent-fill:hover {
				background-color: #0073e6;
				transform: translateY(-1px);
				box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(26, 140, 255, 0.3);
			}

			.ghost-outline {
				background-color: transparent;
				color: #ffffff;
				border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
			}

			.ghost-outline:hover {
				background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
				border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
				transform: translateY(-1px);
			}

			/* Multi-Omics Information Data Grid Block */
			.data-block {
				padding: 8rem 1.5rem;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
				background: linear-gradient(180deg, #000c1a 0%, #001226 100%);
			}

			.grid-container {
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 1200px;
				text-align: center;
			}

			.grid-headline {
				font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
				font-weight: 800;
				margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
				letter-spacing: -0.5px;
			}

			.grid-tagline {
				font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.15rem);
				color: #a0c0e0;
				max-width: 650px;
				margin: 0 auto 4rem auto;
				line-height: 1.6;
			}

			.card-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
				gap: 1.5rem;
			}

			.info-card {
				background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
				border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
				border-radius: 12px;
				padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
				text-align: left;
				transition: all 0.3s ease;
			}

			.info-card:hover {
				background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
				border-color: rgba(26, 140, 255, 0.3);
				transform: translateY(-4px);
			}

			.card-index {
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				color: #1a8cff;
				display: block;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
				letter-spacing: 1px;
			}

			.info-card h3 {
				font-size: 1.3rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
			}

			.info-card p {
				font-size: 0.95rem;
				color: #a0c0e0;
				margin: 0;
				line-height: 1.5;
			}

			@keyframes revealAnim {
				from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); }
				to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<main class="page-container">
			
			<!-- HERO BLOCK -->
			<section class="hero-block">
				<div class="center-content">
					<!-- Loads your uploaded square logo image asset directly -->
					<div class="logo-box">
						<img 
							src="/panoromics-logo.png" 
							alt="PanorOmics Center Logo" 
							class="main-brand-asset" 
						/>
					</div>
					
					<!-- Operational Buttons -->
					<div class="cta-row">
						<a href="#ecosystem" class="nav-button accent-fill">Explore Ecosystem</a>
						<a href="#ecosystem" class="nav-button ghost-outline">Center Research</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- ECOSYSTEM SECTION -->
			<section id="ecosystem" class="data-block">
				<div class="grid-container">
					<h2 class="grid-headline">The Multi-Omics Ecosystem</h2>
					<p class="grid-tagline">Simultaneously analyzing data layers across the central dogma of biology to resolve disease mechanisms.</p>
					
					<div class="card-grid">
						<div class="info-card">
							<span class="card-index">01</span>
							<h3>Genomics</h3>
							<p>Mapping primary DNA structures and inherited structural disease variants.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="info-card">
							<span class="card-index">02</span>
							<h3>Transcriptomics</h3>
							<p>Quantifying static and dynamic cellular RNA gene expression levels.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="info-card">
							<span class="card-index">03</span>
							<h3>Proteomics</h3>
							<p>Characterizing protein expression profiles alongside underlying cellular modifications.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="info-card">
							<span class="card-index">04</span>
							<h3>Bioinformatics</h3>
							<p>Applying innovative data sciences to integrate deep computational multi-omics layers.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

		</main>
	</body>
</html>
